            <td>Deployment Pipeline
            <td>A series of automated steps that packages, tests, and deploys software changes from development to production environments. The aim of the deployment pipeline is to provide the customer with a quick and easy delivery process.
            <td>Andy Corrigan. (July 20, 2022). Deployment pipelines. Octopus. https://octopus.com/devops/continuous-delivery/what-is-a-deployment-pipeline/
          </tr>
